| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7760 — Recovery Inhibition (shinyhunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1d5a8713-0e28-5514-9cf2-c363546fa610"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
